    "Access and modify the master project schedule (e.g., using Primavera P6 or MS Project) to extend the 'Structural Steel Level 4 Fabrication & Delivery' task by 5 days, ensuring all logical dependencies are correctly updated and critical path re-evaluated.",
    "Conduct a comprehensive dependency analysis on all tasks linked to 'Structural Steel Level 4' to identify potential knock-on effects. Review resource loading charts for subsequent phases to pre-empt and mitigate any availability conflicts.",
    "Draft and distribute an official project update notification via email to all identified stakeholders, detailing the approved 5-day delay, its root cause (port strike), revised key milestone dates, and confirming no budget impact.",
